### Find all Ingredients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ingredients?size=30
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: 18d39335-e5a9-4b7f-97d9-a4a03315a000

### Find Ingredient by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ingredients/a8cdfb13-cfef-48bb-ae4e-1da8868215b8
Accept: application/json
X-Request-ID: 18d39335-e5a9-4b7f-97d9-a4a03315a001

### Create Ingredient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ingredients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Tea"
}

### Update Ingredient
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ingredients/287b855b-588f-48d8-94e1-8fef49624a5e
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "version": 2,
    "title": "Black Tea"
}


### Delete Ingredient
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ingredients/287b855b-588f-48d8-94e1-8fef49624a5e?version=3